item.title: Services
item.description: Workforce Optimization We focus on serving our clients with a combination of innovative technologies, increased efficiencies, and leading edge solutions with an end-goal of achieving client excellence. A full assessment from current state staffing spend, rates, inefficiencies, risks and gaps and provides future state recommendations for re-alignment of recruiting methodology, staffing suppliers and support functions. Managed Staffing Programs (MSP) From overall program management, order distribution to consolidated billing across all program suppliers, our proven model incorporates best practices drawn from more than decades of experience.

item.title: Staffing
item.description: Staffing Areas TanPro Technologies is able to provide results custom to your needs and requirements. We understand that your goals will be unique and we are able to provide solutions that are specific to them. Our range of vertical markets has given us the experience needed to help you with your IT staffing requirements, whether it is contract staffing or direct hire. We know that every industry has different requirements and expectations when it comes to IT staffing and we are able to deliver on those needs.
